rs in a shadow dance, a bonfire blazes in the darkness, a trail of artificial lights illuminate a kitsch architectural structure. Creating a montage that takes its rhythms from the waxing and waning motions of the different light sources Austrian artist Lisl Ponger proposes a playful and poetic contemplation of light and shadow and their qualities when captured as cinematic images.</p>", "constellations_primary": [], "constellations_other": [], "recommendations": [], "title_for_label": "<p>Substantial shadows</p>", "creator_credit_for_label": "<p>Lisl Ponger</p>", "headline_credit_for_label": "<p>Austria, 1987</p>", "description": "<p>An elegant, silent meditation on different light forms as they emerge from and transform different obscure, shadowy environments. A miner&#8217;s torch flickers across the walls of a cave, a candle flame flickers in a shadow dance, a bonfire blazes in the darkness, a trail of artificial lights illuminate a kitsch architectural structure. Creating a montage that takes its rhythms from the waxing and waning motions of the different light sources Austrian artist Lisl Ponger proposes a playful and poetic contemplation of light and shadow and their qualities when captured as cinematic images.</p>", "description_for_label": ["<p>An elegant, silent meditation on different light forms as they emerge from and transform different obscure, shadowy environments. A miner&#8217;s torch flickers across the walls of a cave, a candle flame flickers in a shadow dance, a bonfire blazes in the darkness, a trail of artificial lights illuminate a kitsch architectural structure. Creating a montage that takes its rhythms from the waxing and waning motions of the different light sources Austrian artist Lisl Ponger proposes a playful and poetic contemplation of light and shadow and their qualities when captured as cinematic images.</p>"], "credit_line_for_label": "", "details": [{"label": "Language", "display_values": ["German"]}, {"label": "Subject category", 